The mystery is over—Red Hulk’s true identity is finally revealed! In this episode of the Major Issues Podcast, we’re diving into issues #13-24 of Jeph Loeb and Ed McGuinness’ Hulk run, where the truth behind the big red brute comes crashing down. With shocking twists, massive showdowns, and some of the wildest moments in Hulk history, was the big reveal worth the buildup? And how does this era hold up now that we know the truth? Tune in as we break it all down just in time for Big Red's cinematic debut in Captain America Brave New World!

Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

